# Admin (setly.admin)
setly.admin/node_modules/
setly.admin/.next/
setly.admin/out/
setly.admin/build/
setly.admin/.vercel
setly.admin/*.tsbuildinfo
setly.admin/next-env.d.ts
setly.admin/coverage/
